Package: toymodel1
Title: Toy Example Prediction Model for ModelsCloud
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Mohsen", "Sadatsafavi", email = "mohsen.sadatsafavi@ubc.ca",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A minimal, dependency-free example of a prediction model packaged
    for the ModelsCloud platform. Exposes the standard prediction API:
    model_run() and get_sample_input(). Dot-free copy of toy.pred.model,
    intended as a copy-paste template for building new synchronous
    prediction-model packages.
